## Performance Impact Summary

| Metric | Before (Wikimedia) | After (R2 CDN) |
|---|---|---|
| Image source | Wikimedia (unreliable) | Cloudflare R2 CDN (global edge) |
| Format | JPEG/PNG (variable) | Pre-optimized WebP |
| Typical file size | 500KB-2MB | 50-150KB |
| Latency (first byte) | 500-2000ms | 20-50ms |
| Rate limiting | Frequent 429 errors | Never (your own bucket) |
| Broken images | ~30% on any given load | 0% (verified at upload) |
| Next.js processing | On-the-fly optimization | Skip (pre-optimized) |

